{"word":"ἄδοξος","slug":"ἄδοξος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄδοξος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δόξα'><el>δόξα</el></a>\n<p/><i>inglorious, disreputable</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>: —of persons, <i>obscure, ignoble</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ξως</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}